highlights.text: TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #2.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 145 days straight.
“Make Me Feel” by oskar med k is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 16 spots at #44.
“任何天氣” by 張栢芝 is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #84.
